</div>
<div class="bdt-slider-excerpt" data-reveal="reveal-active" data-bdt-slideshow-parallax="x: 300,-300; opacity: 1,1,0">
<p>Erectile dysfunction (ED) is a common condition that affects many men in Ireland. At McCartan&#x2019;s Pharmacy, we offer two over-the-counter treatments for ED, available after a brief, private consultation with our pharmacist &#x2014; no GP visit required.</p>	</div>
<div data-bdt-slideshow-parallax="x: 400,-400; opacity: 1,1,0">
