<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ff2e01c elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-tablet__width-initial &lt;p&gt;Welcome to McCartan&#x2019;s Pharmacy Caring for the Community We aim to provide the best quality pharmaceutical care to all the communities we serve Men&#x2019;s Health Erectile Dysfunction Erectile dysfunction (ED) is a common condition that affects many men in Ireland. At McCartan&#x2019;s Pharmacy, we offer two over-the-counter treatments for ED, available after a brief, private [&#x2026;]&lt;/p&gt;
 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ff2e01c" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" id="&lt;p&gt;Welcome to McCartan&#x2019;s Pharmacy Caring for the Community We aim to provide the best quality pharmaceutical care to all the communities we serve Men&#x2019;s Health Erectile Dysfunction Erectile dysfunction (ED) is a common condition that affects many men in Ireland. At McCartan&#x2019;s Pharmacy, we offer two over-the-counter treatments for ED, available after a brief, private [&#x2026;]&lt;/p&gt;" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<p>McCartan&#x2019;s Pharmacy is a wholly Irish, family-owned company, established in 2000 by Brian McCartan. Initially established in North Dublin, we now have 20 branches across North, South and West Dublin and Kildare.&#xA0;</p>	</div>
</div>
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a445280 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-tablet__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="a445280" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<p>We aim to provide the best quality pharmaceutical care to all the communities we serve through exceptional customer service and a patient-centred emphasis.</p>	</div>
